# From McIntyre file:

```{r}
setwd("C:/Documents and Settings/Owner/My Documents/RESEARCH/Cheryl")
mating <- read.csv("matings.csv", header = TRUE)
library(nlme)
fm1 <- nlme(mating01 ~ SSasymp(male2miss, Asym, R0, lrc),
		data = mating,
            fixed = Asym + R0 + lrc ~ 1,
            random = Asym ~ 1,
		groups = ~female,
            start = c(Asym = 103, R0 = -8.5, lrc = -3.3))
summary(fm1)
fm2 <- update(fm1, random = pdDiag(Asym + lrc ~ 1))
summary(fm2)
```
